enigma_edit.lua.data

Interface Resolver.Constructor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ApiFunction
    Enclosing interface:
    Resolver

    public static interface Resolver.Constructor
extends ApiFunction
    Resolver constructor interface. This interface re-declares the call method to return a resolver. Every class implementing the Resolver interface should have a static method Constructor constructor(), that returns an implementation of this interface.
